title: Jim Butchers The Dresden Files - Fool Moon (01 - 08) (- Nem -)
description: Based on the second book by Jim Butchers series, Harry Dresden is back again except this time he is needed to get to the bottom of a series of murders that maybe happening around a full moon. All signs seem to point to werewolves, But could it be that simple or is there more going on? Harry has to play it cool and use his talents to find out what is going on with these savage killings and catch whoever is doing this before they continue killing
